<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>トップページ</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  </head>

  <body>
    <header 
      class="text-white text-center"
      style="
        background-image: url(<%= asset_path('aomoringolab_top.jpg') %>);
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        min-height: 50vh;
        padding-bottom: 5rem;
        position: relative;
      "
    >
      <div class="container-fluid d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center" style="height: 100%; position: relative; z-index: 2;">
        <%= image_tag("aomoringolab_hakase.png", alt: "りんご博士", class: "ringohakase img-fluid", style: "max-width: 200px; height: auto;") %>
        <h3 class="display-4" style="color: #186779; text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);">ようこそアオモリンゴラボへ</h3>
        <p class="lead" style="color: #186779; text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);">りんごの魅力・アイディアをラボから発信</p>
        <p class="lead" style="color: #186779; text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);">〜青森とりんごを愛する農家と消費者みんなでつながろう盛り上げよう〜</p>
      </div>
      <div style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0; background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.0); z-index: 1;"></div>
    </header>

    <main class="container-xl px-4">
      <div class="row justify-content-center g-4">
        <%# 各カードブロック %>
        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 mb-4">
          <%= link_to guest_sign_in_path, method: :post, class: "card custom-card text-center h-100", style: "background-color: #589ec1; color: white; text-decoration: none;" do %>
            <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center">
              <h5 class="card-title">ゲストユーザーログイン</h5>
            </div>
          <% end %>
          <p class="text-muted text-center" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">アカウントを作らずまずはお試ししてみたい方はこちら</p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 mb-4">
          <%= link_to new_user_session_path, class: "card custom-card text-center h-100", style: "background-color: #589ec1; color: white; text-decoration: none;" do %>
            <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center">
              <h5 class="card-title">ログイン</h5>
            </div>
          <% end %>
          <p class="text-muted text-center" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">アカウントをお持ちの方はこちら</p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 mb-4">
          <%= link_to new_user_registration_path, class: "card custom-card text-center h-100", style: "background-color: #589ec1; color: white; text-decoration: none;" do %>
            <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center">
              <h5 class="card-title">新規登録</h5>
            </div>
          <% end %>
          <p class="text-muted text-center" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">アカウントをお持ちでない方はこちらから登録ください</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row justify-content-center mt-5">
        <div class="col-12 col-md-8">
          <h2 class="mb-4">新着投稿</h2>
          <%= render 'public/posts/index', posts: @posts %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
